      <hedline>
        <hl1>REFRIGERATOR COMPANY SOLD</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <byline class="print_byline">By Sabrina Tavernise</byline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Novolipetsk Metal Factory, Russia, to sell its subsidiary Stinol, Russia's largest refrigerator maker, to Merloni Elettrodomestici of Italy for $119.3 million (S)</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>A Russian steel producer, Novolipetsk Metal Factory, agreed to sell its subsidiary Stinol, Russia's largest refrigerator maker, to Merloni Elettrodomestici of Italy for $119.3 million in one of the biggest purchases by a foreign buyer in Russia's consumer goods industry since the 1998 financial crisis.</p>
        <p>Sabrina Tavernise</p>
      </block>
      <block class="full_text">
